quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,"Uye nyangwe tikavapa tsitsi uye tobvisa matambudziko ari pavari, vanoramba vachingoita zvitadzo zvavo, vachidzungaira vasingadi (chokwadi, vachiita nokusaziva)"
  23,76,"Uye takave tinovabata nemarwadzo (tinovatumira seyambiro), asi havana kuva vanozvininipisa kuna Tenzi vavo, uye havana kusheedza (Allah) vachizvipira kwavari"
  23,77,"Kusvikira\ttavavhurira\tgonhi\tremarwadzo\tmakuru,\tnenguva\tdiki\tvachange\tvarimo vachishungurudzika"
  23,78,"Uye ndivo (Allah) vakakugadzirirai kunzwa (nzeve), nokuona (maziso), uye moyo (kufunga kwakakwana). Asi kashoma pamunopa kutenda"
  23,79,"Uye ndivo (Allah) vanokusikai panyika, uye kwavarizve muchaunganidzwa"
  23,80,"Uye ndivo (Allah) vanopa upenyu uye vokonzera kufa, uye kupindana (kupesana) kweusiku nemasikai ndekwavo (Allah). Saka hamunzwisisiwo here"
  23,81,Asi vanotaura sematauriro evanhu vokutanga ivo vasati vavapo
  23,82,"Vakataura kuti: “Kana tafa tova ivhu nemapfupa, tichamutswa here zvechokwadi?”"
  23,83,"“Zvirokwazvo, takavimbiswa izvi isu nemadzibaba edu kumashure! Izvi hazvisi chimwe chinhu kusara kwengano dzeavo vaivapo kare!”"
  23,84,"Taura kuti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Ndiani muridzi wenyika uye wese arimo, kana muchiziva?”"
  23,85,"Vachataura kuti: “NdiAllah!” Taura kuti: “Saka hamurangarire here?”"
  23,86,"Taura kuti: “Ndiani Tenzi vematenga manomwe, uye Tenzi vechigaro chikuru?”"
  23,87,"Vachataura kuti: “Allah.” Taura kuti: “Saka hamuvatyi here?”"
  23,88,"Taura kuti: “Mumaoko ani mune ushe wezvinhu zvose? Uye vanodzivirira asi ivo hapana anovadzivirira kana muchiziva?”"
  23,89,"Vachataura\tkuti:\t“(Zvese)\tndezva\tAllah.”\tTaura\tkuti:\t“Saka\tsei\tmuchinyengedzwa muchitendeukira chokwadi?”"
  23,90,"Asi tavaunzira chokwadi (Islaam), asi ivo (vasingatendi) zvirokwazvo vanyepi"
  23,91,"Allah havana mwanakomana (kana sikana), kana kuti kune umwe mwari navo. (Dai varipo vanamwari vakawanda), umwe neumwe mwari aizotora izvo zvaakasika, uye vamwe vavo vaizoedza kukunda vamwe. Mukuru ndiAllah vari pamusoro peizvo zvavanovatsanangudza nazvo"
  23,92,(Ndivo) vanoziva izvo zvisingaoneki uye izvo zvinooneka! Saka mukuru ndivo pamusoro peizvo zvavanomusanganisa nazvo
  23,93,"Taura (Muhammad (SAW)) kuti: “Tenzi vangu! Dai mandiratidza izvo zvavakavimbiswa (murango).”"
  23,94,"“Tenzi vangu! Saka (ndinunurei kubva kumurango wenyu), musandiise pakati peavo vanhu vanotadza.”"
  23,95,Uye zvirokwazvo tinokwanisa kukuratidza (Muhammad (SAW)) izvo zvatinovavimbisa
  23,96,Dzivirira zvivi neicho chiri nani. Isu tisu tinoziva izvo zvavanovasanangudza nazvo
  23,97,"Uye taura kuti: “Tenzi vangu! Ndokumbirawo ruponeso kwamuri kubva kune ruzeve-zeve rwemaShayaatween (vanadhiyabhorosi).”"
  23,98,"“Uye ndinokumbira ruponeso maMuri, Tenzi vangu, nyangwe vakavapo pedyo neni.”"
  23,99,"Kusvikira rufu rwauya kune umwe wavo (weavo vasingatendi), anotaura kuti: “Tenzi vangu! Ndidzorereizve (panyika).”"
  23,100,“Kuti ndinoita mabasa akanaka awo andisina kuita kumashure!” Kwete! Mashoko chete aari kutaura; uye kumberi kwavo kune Barzakh (Chidziviso) kusvikira zuva ravachamutswa (kubva kuvafi)
  23,101,"Uye kana hwamanda yaridzwa, hapana hukama uchange huripo pakati pavo pazuva iroro, uye hapana achabvunza umwe pamusoro peumwe"
  23,102,"Uye avo miyero yavo icharema (nezvakanaka), ndivo avo vachabudirira"
  23,103,"Asi avo miyero yavo ichareruka, ndivo vanhu vakazvirasisa pachavo, uye vachava vagari vemuGehena nekusingaperi"
  23,104,"Moto uchapisa zviso zvavo, uye varimo vachasara vakanyenama (miromo yavo yatsva)"
  23,105,"(Kuchataurwa) kuti: “Ndima dzangu hadzina kuverengwa kwamuri here, uye maidziramba?”"
  23,106,"Vachataura kuti: “Tenzi vedu! Kushata kwedu kwave kunotikurira, uye taive vanhu vakarasika.”"
  23,107,"“Tenzi vedu! Tiburitsei mazviri. Uye tikava tinodzekera (kumabasa akaipa), zvirokwazvo, tinenge tiri vanhu vanotadza.”"
  23,108,"Vachataura (Allah) kuti: “Rambai murimo makadzikisirwa, uye musave munotaura neni!”"
  23,109,"Zvirokwazvo, paiva neboka revaranda vangu vaitaura kuti: “Tenzi vedu! Tinotenda, saka tiregererei, uye mova munotinzwira tsitsi, uye ndimi nyanzvi kukunda vese pakunzwira tsitsi!”"
  23,110,"“Asi\tmakavatora\tsechisekwa,\tkusvikira\tvakuitai\tkuti\tmukanganwe\trangariro\tyangu muchivaseka!”"
  23,111,"“Zvirokwazvo, ndavapa makomborero muzuva ranhasi nekuda kwekutsungirira kwavo, kuti zvirokwazvo ndivo vanhu vakabudirira.”"
  23,112,"(Allah) vachataura kuti: “Makagara makore mangani panyika?”"
  23,113,"Vachataura kuti: “Takagara zuva rimwe chete kana chidimbu chezuva. Bvunzai avo vanoverenga.”"
  23,114,"(Allah) vachataura kuti: “Hamuna kugara kusara kwekanguva kadiki kana muchiziva!”"
  23,115,"“Maifunga kuti takakusikai sedambe (pasina chinangwa), uye kuti hamusi kuzodzoswa kwatiri (Allah).”"
  23,116,"Saka mukuru ndiAllah, Mambo vechokwadi! Laa ilaaha illaa Huwa (Hakuna umwe mwari anekodzero yekunamatwa kusara kwavo), Tenzi wechigaro chitsvene"
  23,117,"Uye uyo anonamata umwe mwari kusara kwaAllah asina humboo (nazvo), zvino zvirokwazvo mutongo wake huna Tenzi vake. Zvirokwazvo, avo vasingatendi havabudiriri"
  23,118,"Uye (iwe Muhammad (SAW)) taura kuti: “Tenzi vangu! Regererai uye ivai netsitsi, uye ndimi nyanzvi inokunda vese pakunzwira tsitsi!”"